    <!-- Chosen Palette: Warm Neutrals (Cream/Off-White #FDFCF8) with Dark Charcoal (#1A1A1A) text and Metallic Gold (#C5A059) accents for a premium, trustworthy "Vault" aesthetic. -->
    <!-- Application Structure Plan: 
         1. Hero Section: Uses the core_messaging.md headline/tagline to set the stage.
         2. "The Architecture of Income" (Interactive Grid): Represents the 8 Core Platform Features. Clicking a feature reveals details, replacing a central content area. Purpose: Quick high-level exploration of the system's capabilities.
         3. "Admin Command Center" (Simulation): A Chart.js visualization demonstrating the "Advanced Admin Dashboard" feature. Users can toggle timeframes (Day/Week/Month) to see simulated sales analytics. Purpose: Show, don't just tell, the power of the backend.
         4. "Marketplace Categories" (Filterable Gallery): Displays the product types (AI, Dropshipping, etc.) with interaction to filter by category. Purpose: Showcase the breadth of the catalog.
         5. "Enterprise Security" (Process Flow): A visual, step-by-step breakdown of the secure transaction process.
    -->
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: 
         1. Admin Dashboard Sim (Line Chart): Goal -> Demonstrate "Real-time sales analytics". Interaction -> Timeframe toggles update data. Justification -> A line chart is the industry standard for tracking sales over time.
         2. Marketplace Category Distribution (Doughnut Chart): Goal -> Visualize the diversity of the catalog. Interaction -> Hover for details. Justification -> Shows the "Wide selection" mentioned in the report proportionally.
         3. Feature Grid: Goal -> Organize the 8 distinct platform features. Interaction -> Click to expand details. Justification -> Cleanest way to present a list of complex features without overwhelming text.
         4. Security Flow (Styled HTML Steps): Goal -> Explain "Enterprise-Level Security". Interaction -> Hover to highlight steps. Justification -> Linear process flow is best for transaction security explanation.
         CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. 
    -->
    <!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
